  <ol>
    <li>Open the Benchmarks page</li>
    <li>Click the Refresh button</li>
    <li>Wait a few seconds for rankings to update</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Progress Not Tracking</h2>
  <p>If your runs aren't counting toward benchmark progress:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Make sure you're playing the correct scenario name (exact match required)
    </li>
    <li>Check that runs are appearing in the Scenarios page</li>
    <li>Some benchmarks require specific settings or difficulty modes</li>
  </ul>

